an unsigned commentary in the communist party newspaper peoples 
daily appeared aimed at reassuring chinas educated elite some of 
whom have come under sharp attack for supporting what the party 
calls bourgeois liberalism western liberal ideas and the 
studentled prodemocracy movement 
there has been some concern as to whether the partys policy 
