liberalism will elevate their understanding and continue to make 
contributions to chinas modernization program it said 
the armys violent crackdown on mass demonstrations in early 
june has ushered in a new era of repression chinese are urged to 
turn in friends and family members who participated in the 
protests and many must attend weekly political study sessions 
reminiscent of the ultraleftist cultural revolution 
