in an interview they came got new apartments more quickly than 
estonians and quickly landed places in the governing apparatus 
we want an equal chance to take part in governing estonia 
russian residents want to stop what they see as the baltics 
slide toward independence they claim their rights were undercut by 
laws recently passn for office 
